 we have a very positive impression from Oasis Beach Apartments, Service was good enough. One small reccomendation to hotel management: it would be more confortable if you set up the card readers for entering the hotel from the parking lot instead of ringing the security bell. I would highly reccomend for people seeking HUGE comfortable apartments with close access to the beach.	
